    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Wood board consisting of a number of thin layers of rotary-cut veneers glued together so that the grain of each layer is at right angles to the grain of the adjacent layer.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
